&lt;h1&gt;About the Eames Institute&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Eames Institute of Infinite Curiosity is a nonprofit public charity dedicated to advancing the dynamic legacy of 20th-century designers Ray and Charles Eames. By sharing the things the Eameses made and loved, along with their joyful and rigorous approach to life and work, we seek to inspire creative problem-solving that positively shapes our world.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With our vast collections, digital and print offerings, an extensive program of events, and the Eames Ranch, we aim to demonstrate the enduring value of the Eameses’ philosophy and invite people to explore their curiosity, ask questions, and implement creative solutions to the challenges of today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;About the Role&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Communications Coordinator plays a key role in shaping, maintaining, and elevating the organization’s voice across multiple platforms. This position supports the execution of day-to-day social media and digital communications across our portfolio of growing brands, including Eames Institute, Stout Books, and San Antonio Valley Ranch. The role focuses on bringing social strategies to life through thoughtful planning, content creation, and consistent publishing across platforms including Instagram, LinkedIn, YouTube, Facebook, Pinterest, and TikTok.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Communications Coordinator manages content calendars, writes engaging, on-brand copy, and creates and schedules posts that reflect organizational priorities. This role actively monitors social channels, responds to comments and messages, and fosters an active, responsive online community. Working closely with the Data Analytics Manager, the Coordinator tracks performance metrics, prepares regular reports, and identifies opportunities to improve reach and engagement. Collaborating across marketing, design, and program teams, the Communications Coordinator gathers and develops content to support campaigns, launches, and events. The ideal candidate is highly organized, detail-oriented, attuned to emerging trends, and capable of executing consistently across multiple digital channels.&lt;/p&gt;
