&lt;li&gt;Develop user flows, wireframes, prototypes, and high-fidelity visual design assets that reflect the full context of user engagement, ensuring all digital touchpoints work together to tell a cohesive story.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape core user journeys and champion user-centered design principles to create intuitive, accessible, and delightful experiences across all digital platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
